00:46:39,797 --> 00:46:40,697
I can handle it now.

783
00:46:40,831 --> 00:46:42,800
That man was present
when Dale was shot?

784
00:46:42,932 --> 00:46:45,101
Yeah, Dale was shot
by one of his companions.

785
00:46:45,235 --> 00:46:46,670
Do you recognize this man?

786
00:46:47,036 --> 00:46:48,237
What?

787
00:46:48,371 --> 00:46:50,306
How did my client turn
into a suspect?

788
00:46:51,407 --> 00:46:52,675
I love you so much!

789
00:46:52,809 --> 00:46:57,213
We made a promise:
no lies, no secrets!
